    "en": {
      "title": "\u2018Outstanding Entrepreneur of the Year 2022\u2019 award for Diluni Jayasekara",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "Diluni Jayasekera, Director \u2013 Brand Intelligence of Brand Centrical, was conferred the \u201cOutstanding Entrepreneur of the Year \u2013 2022\u201d award at the Top 50 Professional & Career Women Awards ceremony held in Dubai last month.",
        "Diluni left a marketing career at its peak at a leading agency to co-found Sri Lanka\u2019s first Brand Agency at age 24. Since then, she has contributed tremendously to shaping the new brand-led marketing era of Sri Lanka.",
        "\u2018Diluni is one woman who chose the hard path to success and stood shoulder-to-shoulder with a male counterpart for the last nine years to change the course of a decades-old industry, a press release said.",
        "\u2018Dialog Smart Home brings you a Smart Security Doorbell to ensure the security of your home\u2019",
